# Project Architecture вЂ“ SB Stocks

## Overview

SB Stocks is a web-based paper trading platform that enables users to simulate stock trading using virtual funds and real-time US stock market data. The system follows a three-tier architecture consisting of the Presentation Layer (Frontend), Application Layer (Backend), and Data Layer (Database & External APIs). This architecture ensures scalability, maintainability, and secure communication between components.

