# Advantages of the Architecture

* Modular and easy to maintain
* Scalable for future enhancements
* Secure authentication and authorization
* Efficient communication through REST APIs
* Clear separation of concerns using the MVC design pattern
* Easy integration with third-party stock market APIs
* Supports responsive and user-friendly interfaces

---

# Summary

The SB Stocks architecture is designed using a modern three-tier approach that separates the user interface, business logic, and data management. The React frontend communicates with a Node.js/Express backend through REST APIs, while the backend securely manages user information, portfolio data, and paper trading operations. Real-time stock market information is obtained from external APIs, enabling users to experience realistic stock trading simulations without financial risk.

